      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Features that people would want include validation/autocompletion/quickdocs for <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/arehmandev/736daba40a3e1ef1fbe939c6674d7da8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">the GDSL</a> and integration of <a href=\"https://jenkins.io/doc/book/pipeline/development/#linter\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">the linter</a>. An ideal plugin would make everything &quot;just work&quot; with minimal configuration (e.g. just point it at a Jenkins instance)."
