    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <code>sh</code> like this and the error should go away (worked for me)...</p>\n\n<pre><code>steps {\n    sh \"\"\"\n        echo 'Hello, World!'\n    \"\"\"\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
